---
export const prerender = true;
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import TunnelNav from '../../../components/ui/molecules/TunnelNav.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Site Web IA-first — Étape 1/4 : Le constat · Waimia"
  description="Votre site est un commercial qui dort. Découvrez pourquoi et comment le réveiller avec un agent IA en 4 étapes."
>
  <TunnelNav currentStep={1} />
  <main class="tunnel-page">

    <section class="tnl-hero wrap-wide">
      <p class="tnl-eyebrow reveal">§ Étape 1/4 — Le constat <span aria-hidden="true">·</span> <span lang="en">Step 1/4 — The problem</span></p>
      <h1 class="tnl-h1 reveal-mask-up">
        Votre site est un commercial<br/>
        qui dort. <em>Réveillez-le<br/>avec un agent IA.</em>
        <span lang="en">Your website is a sales rep that sleeps. <em>Wake it up with an AI agent.</em></span>
      </h1>
      <p class="tnl-lede reveal">
        La majorité des sites B2B perdent 70 % de leurs visiteurs en moins de trois secondes — non pas par manque de budget, mais par accumulation silencieuse : CMS trop lent, contenu périmé, pas de suivi IA, équipes débordées. Le résultat : un commercial qui ne rappelle jamais.
        <span lang="en">Most B2B websites lose 70% of visitors in under three seconds — not from lack of budget, but from silent accumulation: slow CMS, stale content, no AI tracking, overloaded teams. The result: a sales rep who never calls back.</span>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="tnl-problems wrap-wide">
      <h2 class="tnl-sh2 reveal">Trois frictions qui tuent la conversion <span lang="en">Three frictions that kill conversion</span></h2>
      <div class="tnl-cards reveal-stagger">
        <div class="tnl-card">
          <div class="tnl-card__num">01</div>
          <div class="tnl-card__kicker">Vitesse &amp; performance <span lang="en">Speed &amp; performance</span></div>
          <h3>Le site charge en 4 secondes.<br/>Le prospect part en 2.</h3>
          <p>WordPress avec 40 plugins : First Contentful Paint à 4,2 s, Lighthouse à 34. Chaque seconde de latence coûte 7 % de conversions. Sans IA, impossible d'automatiser les corrections.</p>
          <p lang="en">WordPress with 40 plugins: FCP at 4.2s, Lighthouse at 34. Each second of latency costs 7% in conversions. Without AI, automating fixes is impossible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tnl-card">
          <div class="tnl-card__num">02</div>
          <div class="tnl-card__kicker">Contenu &amp; SEO manuel <span lang="en">Manual content &amp; SEO</span></div>
          <h3>Un article en 6 semaines.<br/>Vos concurrents en publient 8 par semaine.</h3>
          <p>Le brief, les relectures, le SEO, la mise en ligne : 6 semaines par article. Vos concurrents utilisent des agents IA et publient 8 articles/semaine optimisés pour Google et pour les IA génératives.</p>
          <p lang="en">Brief, revisions, SEO, publishing: 6 weeks per article. Your competitors use AI agents and publish 8 articles/week, optimised for Google and generative AI.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tnl-card">
          <div class="tnl-card__num">03</div>
          <div class="tnl-card__kicker">CRM &amp; relances <span lang="en">CRM &amp; follow-ups</span></div>
          <h3>3 200 leads collectés.<br/>Jamais relancés.</h3>
          <p>Les prospects remplissent des formulaires. Ils attendent. Personne ne les relance dans l'heure — celle où la conversion est 7× plus probable. Sans automatisation CRM IA, le pipeline dort.</p>
          <p lang="en">Prospects fill in forms. They wait. Nobody follows up within the hour — when conversion is 7× more likely. Without AI CRM automation, the pipeline sleeps.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="tnl-promise wrap-wide reveal-blur-clip">
      <p class="tnl-promise__pivot">
        Un seul système. Trois agents IA. Votre site devient une machine à leads qui ne s'arrête jamais.
        <span lang="en">One system. Three AI agents. Your website becomes a lead machine that never stops.</span>
      </p>
      <ul class="tnl-benefits reveal-stagger">
        <li><strong>Vitesse 100/100 Lighthouse</strong> — Astro + React, HTML statique pré-rendu, CDN edge Vercel. <span lang="en"><strong>100/100 Lighthouse</strong> — Astro + React, pre-rendered static HTML, Vercel edge CDN.</span></li>
        <li><strong>8 articles SEO/GEO par mois</strong> — Agent éditeur branché sur votre repo, citations dans les IA génératives. <span lang="en"><strong>8 SEO/GEO articles per month</strong> — Editorial agent wired to your repo, cited in generative AI.</span></li>
        <li><strong>CRM + réseaux automatisés</strong> — Relances dans l'heure, séquences nurturing, posts sociaux générés. <span lang="en"><strong>Automated CRM + social</strong> — Follow-ups within the hour, nurturing sequences, generated social posts.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="tnl-cta wrap-wide reveal">
      <div class="tnl-cta__inner">
        <a href="/offres/site-web-ia-tunnel/mecanique" class="btn-primary">
          Voir comment ça marche →
          <span lang="en">See how it works →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">
          Réserver un audit <span lang="en">Book an audit</span>
        </a>
        <p class="tnl-cta__meta">Étape 1/4 · <span lang="en">Step 1/4</span></p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Base>

<style>
.tunnel-page { padding-block: 0; }
.wrap-wide { max-width: 1200px; margin-inline: auto; padding-inline: clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px); }
.tnl-eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-mono, 'JetBrains Mono', monospace); font-size: clamp(11px, 1.2vw, 13px); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em; color: var(--color-muted, #888); margin-bottom: 24px; padding-top: clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px); }
.tnl-h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif, 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif); font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 80px); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -.02em; color: var(--color-ink, #1a1a1a); margin-bottom: clamp(24px, 4vw, 48px); max-width: 16ch; }
.tnl-h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--color-accent, #C94F2E); }
.tnl-lede { font-family: var(--font-body, 'Inter Tight', sans-serif); font-size: clamp(16px, 1.8vw, 20px); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--color-ink, #1a1a1a); max-width: 62ch; margin-bottom: clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px); }
.tnl-sh2 { font-family: var(--font-serif, 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif); font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 40px); letter-spacing: -.01em; margin-bottom: clamp(32px, 4vw, 56px); color: var(--color-ink, #1a1a1a); }
.tnl-hero { padding-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); }
.tnl-problems { padding-block: clamp(64px, 8vw, 112px); border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.07); }
.tnl-promise { padding-block: clamp(64px, 8vw, 112px); border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.07); background: var(--color-ink, #1a1a1a); border-radius: 2px; margin-block: 1px; }
.tnl-cta { padding-block: clamp(64px, 8vw, 112px); border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.07); }
.tnl-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1px; background: rgba(0,0,0,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; }
.tnl-card { background: var(--color-paper, #F6F1E8); padding: clamp(24px, 3vw, 40px); }
.tnl-card__num { font-family: var(--font-mono, 'JetBrains Mono', monospace); font-size: 11px; color: var(--color-muted, #888); letter-spacing: .08em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.tnl-card__kicker { font-family: var(--font-mono, 'JetBrains Mono', monospace); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; color: var(--color-accent, #C94F2E); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.tnl-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-serif, 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif); font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 24px); line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--color-ink, #1a1a1a); }
.tnl-card p { font-family: var(--font-body, 'Inter Tight', sans-serif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--color-muted, #666); }
.tnl-promise__pivot { font-family: var(--font-serif, 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif); font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 36px); line-height: 1.3; color: var(--color-paper, #F6F1E8); max-width: 52ch; margin-bottom: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px); }
.tnl-benefits { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; padding: 0; }
.tnl-benefits li { font-family: var(--font-body, 'Inter Tight', sans-serif); font-size: 15px; color: rgba(246,241,232,.8); padding-left: 20px; position: relative; }
.tnl-benefits li::before { content: '—'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-accent, #C94F2E); font-family: var(--font-mono, 'JetBrains Mono', monospace); }
.tnl-benefits li strong { color: var(--color-paper, #F6F1E8); }
.tnl-cta__inner { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
.btn-primary { font-family: var(--font-body, 'Inter Tight', sans-serif); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; background: var(--color-ink, #1a1a1a); color: var(--color-paper, #F6F1E8); padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity .2s; }
.btn-primary:hover { opacity: .85; }
.btn-secondary { font-family: var(--font-body, 'Inter Tight', sans-serif); font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-ink, #1a1a1a); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.18); padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: none; transition: border-color .2s; }
.btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--color-ink, #1a1a1a); }
.tnl-cta__meta { font-family: var(--font-mono, 'JetBrains Mono', monospace); font-size: 11px; color: var(--color-muted, #888); letter-spacing: .06em; margin-left: auto; }
[lang="en"] { display: block; font-size: .88em; color: var(--color-muted, #888); margin-top: 4px; font-style: italic; }
</style>
